titleInfo.title: Survey of Tract T-3-S, East Feliciana Parish, Louisiana.

mods.abstract: Undated survey map of East Feliciana Parish. Gives many landowners' names. Bounded on the west by Thompson Creek and the West Feliciana Parish line. Scale not given.
